page.title: 18Listed Buildings/Chelsfield
page.content: {The following buildings have been listed by the S.S.E.and cannot be altered or demolished without specific consent from the Local Authority in liaison with the Greater London Council Historic Buildings Committee} 1.Chelsfield House,Bucks Cross Road. 2.Bucks Cross Cottages,1&2 Bucks Cross. 3.Rose Cottages,3&4, Bucks Cross Road. 4.5&6 Bucks Cross Road. 5.Five Bells Public House Church Road. 6.Chelsfield Post Office Church Road. 7.Cross House,Church Road. 8.Neal's,Church Road. 9.June Cottage,Church Road. 10.Darrickhurst Cottage,Church Road. 11.Julian's Brimstone,Church Road. 12.Wychway,Church Road. 13.The Old Bakery, Church Road. 14.1 2 & 3 Church Road. 15.4 5 & 6 Church Road. 16.Stone House,Church Road.
